      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6 and boil a kettle</p><p>Cover your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> in<strong> cling film</strong> and bash with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until evenly flattened and approx. 1cm in thickness</p>",
