            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped onion</strong> and cook for 5 min until softened, then add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p><p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>with<strong> </strong>50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>water</strong>, your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> </span><strong>sugar </strong>then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium-low and cook for 15 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1933.-step-5-x200.jpg",
