            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the sauce is cooking, add your <strong>wholewheat spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the spaghetti for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving the pot</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1933.-step-6-x200.jpg",
