            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>spinach</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until wilted</p><p>Drain off any excess liquid and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Stir the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>basil</strong> into the<strong> </strong>tomato sauce</p><p>Slice the<strong> lemony chicken Milanese </strong>on a clean board</p>",
      "order": 7,
