      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> tomato sauce</strong> over the <strong>spaghetti</strong> with the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>lemony chicken Milanese</strong> on top and the <strong>wilted</strong> <strong>spinach</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
